## Install

Using [pixi][pixi-url],
install from PyPI with:

```sh
pixi add --pypi {{ project_name }}
```

or install the latest development version from GitHub with:

```sh
pixi add --pypi {{ project_name }}@https://github.com/{{ github_username }}/{{ project_name }}.git
```

Otherwise,
use `pip` or your `pip`-compatible package manager:

```sh
pip install {{ project_name }}  # from PyPI
pip install git+https://github.com/{{ github_username }}/{{ project_name }}.git  # from GitHub
```

